        "content": "<p>Can someone help me understand what  <code>instance-order</code>  means as a value of <code>MedicationOrder.intent</code> ?</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/valueset-medication-request-intent.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/valueset-medication-request-intent.html\">Docs say</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The request represents an instance for the particular order, for example a medication administration record.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 153961905,
        "sender_full_name": "Josh Mandel",
        "timestamp": 1526478885
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>say you have a prescription for 1 tablet  3 times a day for 5 days</p>",
        "id": 153961906,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1526478919
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>ok...</p>",
        "id": 153961907,
        "sender_full_name": "Josh Mandel",
        "timestamp": 1526478940
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>a normal order says \"take this 3 times a day for 5 days\".</p>",
        "id": 153961908,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1526478950
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>OK (<code>\"intent\": \"order\"</code>).</p>",
        "id": 153961909,
        "sender_full_name": "Josh Mandel",
        "timestamp": 1526478973
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>but the nurses's system will get scheduled for the next 5 days, at 7 am, 3 pm, 11 pm..</p>",
        "id": 153961911,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1526479001
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, and those <code>\"intent\": \"instance-order\"</code> requests will match 1:1 to <code>MedicationAdministration</code>s?</p>",
        "id": 153961912,
        "sender_full_name": "Josh Mandel",
        "timestamp": 1526479024
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>so a system will issue 15 medicationrequests, instance-orders</p>",
        "id": 153961913,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1526479029
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yep.</p>",
